| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3688 — Recovery Inhibition (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 5dd46ad0-cddd-5241-8ac1-7df4df01a69f"
